sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我一般會話：「要搵食就唔好撚讀哲學啦！」</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好似Thales咁攞哲學黎搵食先至霸氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我未聽過thales要搵食喎果個時代"},{"pid":"7bd8d5a76e4ee2311164fdcf7a9125e6abddffe4","tid":60819,"uid":12140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T06:45:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>認真一問 學嚟有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最高級嘅知識就係最唔實用嘅知識<br />\n呢啲係有錢人嘅玩意嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我一般會話：「要搵食就唔好撚讀哲學啦！」</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好似Thales咁攞哲學黎搵食先至霸氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n攞哲學嚟搵食係最差嘅<br />\n你睇下Russell,Wittgenstein幾時煩過錢銀<br />\n班大學教授夠日日搵食啦"},{"pid":"f15f0cfbd7f16ed725fa2ff87861deda052ebd35","tid":60819,"uid":12140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T06:46:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我好懷疑有冇Acquaintance Knowledge呢種知識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有人會claim當Mary離開房間後，佢得到呢種知識。但我好懷疑。至少呢個三分法係好controversial</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你睇下羅素篇原文<br />\n再argue against"},{"pid":"ab1b701131c5547f2efbf702dff669d0eee19bed","tid":60819,"uid":2438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T06:54:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我好懷疑有冇Acquaintance Knowledge呢種知識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有人會claim當Mary離開房間後，佢得到呢種知識。但我好懷疑。至少呢個三分法係好controversial</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你睇下羅素篇原文<br />\n再argue against</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nFine咁我自已睇，唔需要討論"},{"pid":"abe67d0204ea049319f0fb6852ad25097b453fcc","tid":60819,"uid":12140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T06:57:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我好懷疑有冇Acquaintance Knowledge呢種知識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有人會claim當Mary離開房間後，佢得到呢種知識。但我好懷疑。至少呢個三分法係好controversial</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你睇下羅素篇原文<br />\n再argue against</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nFine咁我自已睇，唔需要討論</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我嘅意思係<br />\n睇完再討論<br />\n否則會好冇效率<br />\n因為大家都唔知對方講咩<br />\n冇foundation討論係冇用㗎<br />\n讀哲學就會明"},{"pid":"317373a7b4fd078176405f22a1d775f6ac4a7d8f","tid":60819,"uid":64966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T08:32:07.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"a79f22d87bb1a0a0bc9b1f5f05236e9a8eeb0910","tid":60819,"uid":12140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T08:43:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你睇下羅素篇原文<br />\n再argue against</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nFine咁我自已睇，唔需要討論</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我嘅意思係<br />\n睇完再討論<br />\n否則會好冇效率<br />\n因為大家都唔知對方講咩<br />\n冇foundation討論係冇用㗎<br />\n讀哲學就會明</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實再進一步嚟講<br />\n你要明羅素於知識論嘅立場係foundationalism（justification）<br />\n即係話，佢認為知識同justified belief應該係要有個foundation<br />\n而acq就係佢講嘅foundation"},{"pid":"b1df268af919bc36cd2b84850ddec7c72d4146af","tid":60819,"uid":349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T14:20:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最高級嘅知識就係最唔實用嘅知識<br />\n呢啲係有錢人嘅玩意嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我一般會話：「要搵食就唔好撚讀哲學啦！」</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好似Thales咁攞哲學黎搵食先至霸氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我未聽過thales要搵食喎果個時代</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好似又唔太算用哲學搵食既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n觀星睇睇下跌左落井，路過個呀嬸話：你睇下你，睇星睇到腳下有咩都唔知<br />\n之後佢睇星預知橄欖失收（好似係）之後屯積橄欖賺左筆"},{"pid":"561fa86fb99aba2f44c99f39663cfd24586834fc","tid":60819,"uid":12140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-02T00:00:41.000Z","msg":"承上一章，今次要講下truth呢樣嘢，truth中文通常會譯做真理，但係可能因為啲基督教(以防大家唔知，即係新教加天主教)成日講道路、真理、生命，令到真理聽起上嚟好似好厲害咁，其實喺哲學層面嚟講，truth可以話只係true statement咁解，當然，咁講未必係完全正確嘅，我哋跟住落嚟會探討下the notion of truth，相信會引起大家對truth更多嘅懷惑。<br />\n Truth同knowledge呢兩個notion其實息息相關，由我哋冇可能知道錯嘅嘢呢點上，佢哋嘅關係可見一班。例如我冇可能知道2+2=3，因為2+2=4[1]。而我哋可以咁講：<br />\n如果我知道P，則P。 (If I know p, then p.)<br />\n例如：如果我知道甘迺迪於1963年被行刺，則甘迺迪於1963年被行刺。<br />\n可以話，大多數嘅哲學家都認為truth condition is a necessary condition of knowledge。<br />\n當然，既然講得大多數，就自然有啲哲學家唔認同呢樣嘢，而我哋之後都會講到呢啲睇法。<br />\n既然講到truth同knowledge嘅關係咁密切，咁理解truth亦自然有助我哋理解knowledge。<br />\n而喺講truth嘅性質前，自然要講下Truth嘅載體(Bearer of truth)，要喺呢個之前，又要講下真確值係咩嚟(truth-value)。我哋話一句陳述句就係一句有真確值嘅說話，即係話呢個說話有對錯之分，可能為真或者錯。一個問題，如食咗飯未，唔會有對錯；一句祈使句，如食飯呀，亦唔會有對錯；但係一句陳述句，如你食咗飯，就會係一係啱一係錯。而任何句子只要係either true of false嘅話，咁佢就有真確值，就係陳述句。<br />\n而要搵truth嘅載體好簡單，即係搵佢嘅呈現方式，而所有有真確值嘅嘢都有可能係佢嘅載體，而之所以唔係全部都係，就係因為truth嘅載體應該係一樣比較fundamental嘅嘢，而我哋所有嘅candidates都係互相有一定關係嘅，即係話只要其中一個係載體，咁就好有可能解釋到曬佢哋真確值嘅來源。 (待續)<br />\n<br />\n[1]: Segal. A. (2010) 2+2=4 : <a href=\"http://www.cs.yale.edu/homes/as2446/224.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cs.yale.edu%2Fhomes%2Fas2446%2F224.pdf&d=1MCoT%2FhTd4kw4BoMO5Iu%2FYscwJTI%2BQouKF8MUrnyvY0%3D&h=7671124c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.cs.yale.edu/homes/as2446/224.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"760803d07d370841638715dac6826beb5e3eb21b","tid":60819,"uid":68192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-02T03:26:54.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"a7ad56af465f88d1e803ea593196b849bd9354fa","tid":60819,"uid":4955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-02T03:55:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99543f81e10de1b752203a818979b67c02c463cd","tid":60819,"uid":12140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-02T07:29:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccedac51e99380b8fab7d773ad45c6f5bab6e586","tid":60819,"uid":8428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-02T07:39:38.000Z","msg":"留名學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcd456f7126d98a5a3796de06babecda8e0e38eb","tid":60819,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-02T07:48:08.000Z","msg":"留名學野"},{"pid":"4c15e725c53609e6d25762ea69d878fbda34824d","tid":60819,"uid":67210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-02T08:10:09.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"a4e6f8fa52b39add0a7861b961f80e08cfba7e8d","tid":60819,"uid":43331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-02T08:24:36.000Z","msg":"留名學野 <br />\n<br />\n不過可唔可以prove read 先放出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aca0580588965e432ba8ffb53a1e9508a73a16f4","tid":60819,"uid":12140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-02T08:51:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名學野 <br />\n<br />\n不過可唔可以prove read 先放出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n？<br />\n有咩錯字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好意思<br />\n下次注意返"},{"pid":"353de4b7b9d7ac1e4de91cc8e2d0984ef9536910","tid":60819,"uid":2438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-02T09:12:13.000Z","msg":"哲學仔fb個page是咪都係你？"},{"pid":"fef931ebefe7d37824b37d292d19b49745076eb3","tid":60819,"uid":12140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-02T09:54:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>哲學仔fb個page是咪都係你？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係呀<br />\n話說上次咁答你真係唔好意思<br />\n我有少少社交障礙，所以語氣有時會比較差<br />\n我有講返點解會有acquaintance knowledge 呢樣嘢<br />\n可以睇返上面"},{"pid":"1f816e412bad4d94e774ff73e16483ca4a59c70f","tid":60819,"uid":65736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-02T10:51:16.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"d6c1234350f91867ff668edf4b4c533975b5a463","tid":60819,"uid":2438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-02T14:00:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>哲學仔fb個page是咪都係你？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係呀<br />\n話說上次咁答你真係唔好意思<br />\n我有少少社交障礙，所以語氣有時會比較差<br />\n我有講返點解會有acquaintance knowledge 呢樣嘢<br />\n可以睇返上面</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我自己都有發脾氣，所以都有啲唔好意思<br />\n不打不相識，大家都係哲學系，冇計啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06d235a4e0a65ef675692c4d1ac232b7e4899de3","tid":60819,"uid":12140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-03T06:38:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cb002df8ef9421adfac25063e568eec99fb129f","tid":60819,"uid":44119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-04T04:10:26.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"b0c98249b357284994e8cd19b09932924979e3f5","tid":60819,"uid":7551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-08T10:10:40.000Z","msg":"垃圾哲學仆街<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nLM <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fc138756af508cf5df5fe32a4fc5f266d16bf81","tid":60819,"uid":6537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-08T13:28:29.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22e43892019a1d67f9e51bdf4470c3195cc0684a","tid":60819,"uid":73438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-09T05:01:16.000Z","msg":"想問問樓主，以下對a priori 同 a posteriori 嘅理解岩唔岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？間唔時就會接觸到呢兩個term，但又唔知自己有無理解錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nA priori（中文係先驗？），意思即係唔需要拎實物嚟檢驗一個命題嘅直確值。例如「阿媽係女人」，唔需要真係逐個逐個阿媽check下係咪女人先證明到呢個命題嘅直確值。而基本上所有定義嘅statement 都係呢一類。<br />\n<br />\nA posteriori，就係要睇下現實世界相對應嘅實物同命運相唔相乎，嚟決定嗰個命題嘅直確值。例如「依家個雪櫃有罐啤酒」，咁就要真係去個雪櫃到check 下係咪真係有罐啤酒喺度，先決定到呢個命題嘅直確值。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f218623791f13967c18bd47390138f3d1ed3834","tid":60819,"uid":12140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-09T05:54:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問問樓主，以下對a priori 同 a posteriori 嘅理解岩唔岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？間唔時就會接觸到呢兩個term，但又唔知自己有無理解錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nA priori（中文係先驗？），意思即係唔需要拎實物嚟檢驗一個命題嘅直確值。例如「阿媽係女人」，唔需要真係逐個逐個阿媽check下係咪女人先證明到呢個命題嘅直確值。而基本上所有定義嘅statement 都係呢一類。<br />\n<br />\nA posteriori，就係要睇下現實世界相對應嘅實物同命運相唔相乎，嚟決定嗰個命題嘅直確值。例如「依家個雪櫃有罐啤酒」，咁就要真係去個雪櫃到check 下係咪真係有罐啤酒喺度，先決定到呢個命題嘅直確值。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nA piori即係 independent of experience 普遍嚟講認為數學同邏輯事實都係喺當中之列，例如你講嘅阿媽係女人，同埋英文入面好常見嘅例子：all unmarried men are bachelors ，呢啲都係除咗學習用嚟表達呢啲命題嘅一隻語言嘅經驗外，乜經驗都唔使嘅知識嚟。<br />\nA posteriori就係基於經驗嘅，你講嘅例子就係，而一啲歷史事實，基於經驗/記憶嘅推測，對於現在嘅認知，我認為都喺a posteriori 之列。"},{"pid":"8ab61e6069104d0564b813b28e57b855bb1dabdf","tid":60819,"uid":71140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-09T06:52:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"057429181a5e2160bbc44cf1716b1f72ddd56955","tid":60819,"uid":12140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-09T06:58:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>知唔知邊到有中文既哲學書？<br />\n去圖書館搵極都搵唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實你問十個讀哲學嘅人，九個都應該會答你睇英文<br />\n因為英文真係豐富好多<br />\n不過我知有幾本書都有中譯版<br />\n例如Michael Sandel嘅正義、錢買不到的東西同反對完美都係可以用嚟做政治哲學同道德哲學嘅啟蒙讀物<br />\n仲有本what does it all mean？都有中譯<br />\n不過唔記得咩名，呢本係一本哲學入門，根本上最大路嘅幾個課題都有講"},{"pid":"c6e9f84b41504b6b8335db174b2d71b5c751ead1","tid":60819,"uid":71140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-09T07:25:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"29baa707c9dbcd2ca55c38cd2baa492b538d0f8e","tid":60819,"uid":48729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T05:16:20.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n同埋執錯字先：proofread 呀，唔係 prove read"},{"pid":"89f8931b8915b09dd79259efdf7491370a382200","tid":60819,"uid":42586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T07:59:14.000Z","msg":"pish"}]}